OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FThe legislation will give powers to a
OL,7,Fbody, which is separate from both
OL,8,Fgovernment and football authorities,
OL,9,Fto license clubs in England's top five
OL,10,Ftiers.
OL,12,FFirst pitched nearly five years ago,
OL,13,Fit has been heralded as the possible
OL,14,Fsolution to fixing "the game's broken
OL,15,Ffinancial model".
OL,17,FBut why is a regulator being
OL,18,Fintroduced? And what powers will it
OL,19,Fhave in reality? ITV News explains.
OL,21,FWhat is the new legislation?
