OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FThe legislation underpins the creation
OL,7,Fof the Independent Football Regulator
OL,8,F(IFR) for English football, which will
OL,9,Flicense clubs in the top five tiers of
OL,10,FEnglish football.
OL,12,FAmong the regulator's key
OL,13,Fresponsibilities is ensuring clubs are
OL,14,Ffinancially sustainable, making the
OL,15,Fsport more financially resilient
OL,16,Fbetween leagues and safeguarding
OL,17,FEnglish football's heritage.
OL,19,FWhy is it being introduced?
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G3/18
