OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FA fan-led review of English football's
OL,7,Fgovernance was promised by the
OL,8,FConservative Party in its manifesto
OL,9,Ffor the General Election in 2019,
OL,10,Fwhich came months after the financial
OL,11,Fdemise of Bury.
OL,13,FThe review was commissioned in April
OL,14,F2021 in the immediate aftermath of the
OL,15,FEuropean Super League scandal. Its key
OL,16,Frecommendation was the creation of an
OL,17,Findependent regulator.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G4/18
