OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FThe Conservative government, which
OL,7,Fintroduced the bill, had long warned
OL,8,Ffootball authorities that a regulator
OL,9,Fwould have 'backstop powers' to settle
OL,10,Fthe ongoing row over financial
OL,11,Fdistribution between the Premier
OL,12,FLeague and the EFL (English Football
OL,13,FLeague).
OL,15,F"These powers mean that if the leagues
OL,16,Ffail to agree on a new deal on
OL,17,Ffinancial distributions, then the
OL,18,Fbackstop can be triggered to ensure a
OL,19,Fsettlement is reached," the then
OL,20,Fgovernment said when the bill was
OL,21,Fannounced in early 2024.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G6/18
