OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FLabour amendments confirmed these
OL,7,Fbackstop powers will be in place, to
OL,8,Fbe used as a 'last resort' and only
OL,9,Fwhen certain thresholds have been met.
OL,11,FUnder the new system, the two leagues
OL,12,Fwould each submit their proposal, the
OL,13,Fregulator would assess them against
OL,14,Fpredetermined criteria, and then would
OL,15,Fchoose and impose one as the binding
OL,16,Farrangement.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G7/18
