OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FPrimarily, the regulator will, once
OL,7,Festablished, be concerned with
OL,8,Fsafeguarding the financial
OL,9,Fsustainability of clubs in England
OL,10,Fthrough a licensing system - covering
OL,11,Fclubs from the National League up to
OL,12,Fthe Premier League.
OL,14,FNon-compliance with this would result
OL,15,Fin the regulator inflicting a fine of
OL,16,Fup to 10% of turnover on clubs.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                    G8/18
