OL,3,CIndependent Football Regulator becomes
OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FPowers to assess prospective new
OL,7,Fowners and directors, and disqualify
OL,8,Fthem where they persistently or
OL,9,Fwillfully fail to comply with
OL,10,Flicensing conditions, will also be
OL,11,Favailable to the regulator.
OL,13,FIf an English club were to try and
OL,14,Fsell or relocate its stadium, it would
OL,15,Frequire pre-approval by the regulator.
OL,17,FHowever, the regulator will have no
OL,18,Frole in 'on-pitch' matters or football
OL,19,Fsporting rules.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                   G10/18
