OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,FThe IFR will also have to periodically
OL,7,Fprepare and publish a 'State of Game'
OL,8,Freport, which will provide an
OL,9,Fobjective analysis of the industry.
OL,11,FIn response to the bill receiving
OL,12,Froyal assent on Monday, Prime Minister
OL,13,FKeir Starmer said: "This is a proud
OL,14,Fand defining moment for English
OL,15,Ffootball.
OL,17,F"As someone who has loved the game all
OL,18,Fmy life, I know just how deeply it
OL,19,Fruns through our communities. It's
OL,20,Fwhere memories are made, and
OL,21,Fgenerations come together.
OL,1,W~s1{$~k4{$k7                   G11/18
