OL,4,Claw, but what powers will it have?
OL,6,F"Our landmark Football Governance Act
OL,7,Fdelivers on the promise we made to
OL,8,Ffans. It will protect the clubs they
OL,9,Fcherish, and the vital role they play
OL,10,Fin our economy.
OL,12,F"Through our Plan for Change, we are
OL,13,Fushering in a stronger, fairer future
OL,14,Ffor the game we all love."
OL,16,FThe Football Supporters' Association
OL,17,F(FSA) said it was a "historic moment
OL,18,Ffor football in this country".
