OL,6,F"We are very proud that the FSA was at
OL,7,Fthe heart of change, helping to bring
OL,8,Fin laws which can help protect the
OL,9,Fclubs we love from the worst excesses
OL,10,Fof owners throughout the professional
OL,11,Fgame," said the FSA's chief executive
